This paper is about personalized search story recommendation within a search engine, which involves modeling user behavior and interests. This falls under the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. The proposed approach uses deep reinforcement learning, which involves training a neural network to make decisions based on rewards and punishments, and can be categorized under Machine Learning (cs.LG), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories.
